OL,17,     GArdingly in West Sussex. Kate
OL,18,     GBliss and Gary Pe guide the
OL,19,     Gteams, and presenter Eric Knowles
OL,20,     Glearns how lightweight baskets
OL,21,     Gcalled trugs are made.
